msgid ""
"Usage: xnec2c [options] [<input-file-name>]\n"
"  -i|--input         <input-file-name>\n"
"  -c|--config        <config-file-path>     - file must exist\n"
"  -C|--new-config    <new-config-file-path> - creates the file when missing\n"
"  -j|--jobs  <number of processors in SMP machine> (-j0 disables forking)\n"
"     --openblas-threads <n>  set OpenBLAS thread count (default: 1)\n"
"     --mkl-threads <n>       set Intel MKL thread count (default: 1)\n"
"     --omp-threads <n>       set OpenMP thread count (default: 1)\n"
"  -b|--batch:        enable batch mode, exit after the frequency loop runs\n"
"  -P|--no-pthreads:  disable pthreads and use the GTK loop for debugging\n"
"  -h|--help:         print usage information and exit\n"
"  -V|--version:      print xnec2c version number and exit\n"
"  -v|--verbose:      increase verbosity, can be specified multiple times\n"
"  -d|--debug:        enable debug output (-dd includes backtraces)\n"
"  -d|--quiet:        suppress debug/verbose output\n"
"\n"
"  --optimize:        Activate the optimizer immediately.\n"
"  --skip-verify:     skip geometry verification checks\n"
"  --mem-report:      report managed allocator live bytes per call site\n"
"\n"
"The following arguments write to an output file after the frequency loop\n"
"completes.  These are useful to combine with --batch; If you wish to "
"specify\n"
"filenames to write without --batch mode then enable the File->Optimizer\n"
"Settings or the files you specify on the command line will not be written.\n"
"\n"
"  --write-csv             <filename>  - write CSV file of measurements\n"
"  --write-s1p             <filename>  - write S1P file of S-parameters\n"
"  --write-s2p-max-gain    <filename>  - write S2P file, port-2 is max-gain\n"
"  --write-s2p-viewer-gain <filename>  - write S2P file, port-2 is viewer-"
"gain\n"
"  --write-rdpat           <filename>  - write CSV of the radiation pattern\n"
"  --write-currents        <filename>  - write CSV of currents and charges\n"
"  --write-gnuplot-structure <filename> - write gnuplot structure file\n"
"  --write-patch-currents  <filename>  - write CSV of patch surface currents\n"
"  --write-validation-dir <directory> - write full validation data tree\n"
msgstr ""
"Kasutamine: xnec2c [valikud] [<sisendfaili-nimi>]\n"
"  -i|--input         <sisendfaili-nimi>\n"
"  -c|--config        <konfiguratsioonifaili-tee>     - fail peab olema "
"olemas\n"
"  -C|--new-config    <uue-konfiguratsioonifaili-tee> - loob faili, kui "
"puudub\n"
"  -j|--jobs  <protsessorite arv SMP masinas> (-j0 keelab hargnemise)\n"
"     --openblas-threads <n>  määra OpenBLAS lõimede arv (vaikimisi: 1)\n"
"     --mkl-threads <n>       määra Intel MKL lõimede arv (vaikimisi: 1)\n"
"     --omp-threads <n>       määra OpenMP lõimede arv (vaikimisi: 1)\n"
"  -b|--batch:        luba pakkrežiim, välju pärast sagedustsükli lõppu\n"
"  -P|--no-pthreads:  keela pthreads ja kasuta silumiseks GTK tsüklit\n"
"  -h|--help:         kuva kasutusteave ja välju\n"
"  -V|--version:      kuva xnec2c versiooninumber ja välju\n"
"  -v|--verbose:      suurenda üksikasjalikkust, saab määrata mitu korda\n"
"  -d|--debug:        luba silumisväljund (-dd sisaldab tagasijälgi)\n"
"  -d|--quiet:        summuta silumis-/üksikasjalik väljund\n"
"\n"
"  --optimize:        Aktiveeri optimeerija kohe.\n"
"  --skip-verify:     jäta geomeetria kontroll vahele\n"
"  --mem-report:      teatab hallatava eraldaja elusaid baite kutsekoha "
"kohta\n"
"\n"
"Järgmised argumendid kirjutavad väljundfaili pärast sagedustsükli\n"
"lõppu.  Need on kasulikud koos --batch valikuga; Kui soovite määrata\n"
"failinimed kirjutamiseks ilma --batch režiimita, siis lubage Fail-"
">Optimeerija\n"
"seaded, vastasel juhul käsureal määratud faile ei kirjutata.\n"
"\n"
"  --write-csv             <failinimi>  - kirjuta mõõtmiste CSV-fail\n"
"  --write-s1p             <failinimi>  - kirjuta S-parameetrite S1P-fail\n"
"  --write-s2p-max-gain    <failinimi>  - kirjuta S2P-fail, port-2 on max-"
"gain\n"
"  --write-s2p-viewer-gain <failinimi>  - kirjuta S2P-fail, port-2 on viewer-"
"gain\n"
"  --write-rdpat           <failinimi>  - kirjuta kiirgusdiagrammi CSV\n"
"  --write-currents        <failinimi>  - kirjuta voolude ja laengute CSV\n"
"  --write-gnuplot-structure <failinimi> - kirjuta gnuplot struktuurifail\n"
"  --write-patch-currents  <failinimi>  - kirjuta pinnvoolude CSV\n"
"  --write-validation-dir <kataloog> - kirjuta täielik valideerimisandmete "
"puu\n"

